race.comment: HELLINDA (9) keeps racing well without winning. He was accepted at three venues and is suited here and jumps from an inside gate. The in-form Boudvillian sticks aboard off the Cootamundra placing. The Seib yard has been placing its horses well. MARVEL MAN (5) just missed the hat-trick at Mudgee improving his numbers again. Costin will use the low gate and the speedy galloper will get every chance to bounce. A threat. GRINS (2) was quickly back on track narrowly beaten at Dubbo. That reads well enough and she can get a cosier run from the better gate. Cahill is a key jockey switch replacing the 3kg apprentice. DESTINY'S BOUNTY (1) is going well enough but carries more weight at this level the wsith 4kg claim included. Can't be ruled out all the same.
